# Engineering Concepts Implemented

## Drilling KPIs

- Mechanical Specific Energy (MSE)
- Rate of Penetration (ROP)
- Weight on Bit (WOB)
- Rig State Classification

## Data Engineering

- ETL Pipelines
- SQL Window Analytics
- Data Normalization
- Automated File Tracking

## AI & Automation

- Prompt Engineering
- Generative AI Reporting
- Automated Operational Diagnostics
- Engineering Recommendation Systems

